      "author": "demian0311",
      "description": "## Fixed\n\n- **Pyramid diagrams no longer clip their right-column descriptions.** Bumps `@diagrammo/dgmo` to 0.25.3, whose embed bounding-box estimator now honors `text-anchor` — previously start-anchored description text was under-measured and clipped when the diagram scaled to fit the note width.\n- Edit-link icon repositioned to the bottom-right so it no longer overlaps Obsidian's edit-block button.\n\n## Changed\n\n- Tightened the README and plugin description; removed the awkward inline `` ```dgmo `` code-pill from the intro.\n\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/diagrammo/obsidian-dgmo/compare/1.5.21...1.5.22",
