      "author": "demian0311",
      "description": "### Fixed\n\n- **Word-cloud diagrams no longer collapse to a single giant clipped title** in the reading view. Bumped `@diagrammo/dgmo` to 0.25.2: the embed normalizer no longer trusts a measured content box that covers less than half the canvas (word-cloud words are transform-positioned and invisible to the string bbox estimator, so only the title was measured).\n\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/diagrammo/obsidian-dgmo/compare/1.5.20...1.5.21",
