      "author": "demian0311",
      "description": "### Fixed\n\n- **Embedded diagrams no longer clip in the reading view.** Wide/tall diagrams (ER tables, mindmap nodes, flowchart elements) were being cut off at the right/bottom edge because the shared embed normalizer could override a diagram's correct viewBox with an out-of-bounds estimate. Bumped `@diagrammo/dgmo` to 0.25.1, which only tightens the viewBox when it's a genuine sub-rectangle of the diagram's canvas.\n- **Map diagrams now render mountain relief.** The `mountain-ranges` geo asset is now bundled into the plugin; relief is on by default for maps in dgmo 0.25.x, but the asset wasn't shipped, so Obsidian maps rendered flat.\n\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/diagrammo/obsidian-dgmo/compare/1.5.19...1.5.20",
