      "description": "Bundles `@diagrammo/dgmo@^0.17.0` — [sequence participant types trimmed from 9 → 4 + default](https://github.com/diagrammo/dgmo/releases/tag/v0.17.0).\n\n### Breaking surface for users\n\nNotes containing DGMO sequence diagrams with `is a service` / `is a frontend` / `is a networking` / `is a gateway` / `is a external` will surface `E_PARTICIPANT_TYPE_REMOVED` after the plugin updates. Drop the override — the participant renders as the default rectangle.\n\n### Internal sweep\n\n- Bundled example note's checkout flow no longer carries removed-type overrides on `App` or `Stripe`.",
